=== Database recreation ===
= persistence.xml =
There should be either no value for the parameter javax.persistence.schema-generation.database.action or it should be "none"

* Located in the "Other Sources" package "src/main/resources" folder "META-INF"



= Test class LoadFlickrPhotosJUnitTest =
All test methods should be ignored


* Located in the "Test Packages" package "<default package>"






=== Change database settings ===

= persistence.xml =
* Located in the "Other Sources" package "src/main/resources" folder "META-INF"

= applicationContext-persistence.xml =
* Located in the "Web Pages" folder "WEB-INF"


